Package: RESRECT
Title: Recorrecting Effect-size and Significance with Rank-based Evaluation of Confounds in Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ethan Fenton
Maintainer: Ethan Fenton <ethanfenton27@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Ethan", "Fenton", , "ethanfenton27@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-1945-7517"))
Description: Correct for batch variation in single cell transcriptomics differential expression testing by scaling the expression level ranks of each gene within each sample and cell type to their respective median. 
